EstablishmentDetail.RightToReply: <p> We take food safety standards extremely seriously and are disappointed with the rating that has been given. Since the inspection we have already implemented a number of measures including the appointment of a new senior catering manager, upgrades to fridges and freezers and the launch of an enhanced team training program to improve standards. We are already seeing progress in hygiene practices and the condition and cleanliness of the kitchen. This rating does not meet the standard that we pride ourselves on delivering. We will continue to work with the Local Authority to ensure the previous positive rating is restored as soon as possible.</p>
